---
import "../styles/global.css";

import Page from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Page
  title="Sweet Bakes Chicago - Our Story, Mission, and Passion for Baking."
  description="Learn about the history of Sweet Bakes Chicago and our dedication to ingredients that are nut free and allergy friendly!"
>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 space-y-10">
  <!-- Nut-free notice -->
  <section class="prose prose-lg">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">We Are A 100% Nut Free Facility!</h1>
    <p>
      Sweet Bakes Chicago LLC is a cottage bakery located on the northwest side of Chicago. We
      currently serve the northwest city and neighboring suburbs.
    </p>

    <p>
      Enjoying treats with food allergies can be a challenge.
      <strong>Sweet Bakes Chicago is a Tree Nut and Peanut FREE Facility.</strong>
      We take very special care to be sure that all of our ingredients are not only free of all
      nuts but also not processed in a facility that also processes nuts.
    </p>

    <p>
      We also have gluten, dairy, and sugar free options available for select products. Please
      contact us with any questions — we want to help.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
      Our products are produced in a home kitchen that is not inspected by a health department and
      that may also process common food allergens. If you have safety concerns, contact your local
      health department. Our facility may contain wheat, milk, soy, egg, and shellfish.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- About Me -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-cream  border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
    <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-800">
      <!-- Left-floating image (mobile: centered above text) -->
      <img src="/sara.avif" alt="Sara Williams demure"
        class="w-40 h-40 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-4 block md:float-left md:mr-6 md:mb-2 mx-auto md:mx-0" />
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">About Me</h2>

      <p class="mt-3">
        My name is Sara Williams. I have been baking and decorating treats for over 20 years. I have
        taken classes with Collette Peters of the Food Network, as well as multiple online classes
        taught by world renowned decorators and pastry chefs. I first started decorating in high
        school just to pass time in the summer and quickly grew to love it.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-3">
        I am married and have two children, so I’m currently working out of my home in order to spend
        more time with my family. In 2015, my daughter was diagnosed with a tree nut allergy after
        having a bad reaction to a pistachio. I quickly realized the need for safe and delicious
        treats and made Sweet Bakes Chicago a nut free bakery. As the business grows, and my kids get
        older, I want to expand into a shop outside of my home.
      </p>

      <!-- Right-floating image near the end of the bio (mobile: centered) -->
      <img src="/williams-family-roadtrip.avif" alt="Williams Family at the park smiling"
        class="w-40 h-40 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-sm mt-4 block md:float-right md:ml-6 md:mt-2 mx-auto md:mx-0" />

      <p class="mt-3">
        We specialize in cakes, cookies, donuts, pies and custom event treats. We carefully select
        ingredients that are free from nuts and sourced from nut-free manufacturers whenever possible.
        If you have specific dietary concerns (gluten, dairy, sugar), please let us know — we offer
        select options and will always work with you to create something safe and delicious.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-3">
        Our products are produced in a home kitchen that is not inspected by a health department and
        that may also process common food allergens. If you have safety concerns, contact your local
        health department. Our facility may contain wheat, milk, soy, egg, and shellfish.
      </p>

      <!-- Clear floats before the image row -->
      <div class="clear-both"></div>

      <!-- 3-up image row -->
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <img src="/williams-children-red-bush.avif" alt="Custom cake example"
          class="h-full w-auto object-cover rounded-lg shadow-sm" />
        <img src="/williams-family-at-park.avif" alt="Decorated cookies example"
          class="h-full w-auto object-cover rounded-lg shadow-sm" />
        <img src="/Dlux-and-sara-beach.avif" alt="Cupcakes example" class=" h-autow-auto rounded-lg shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we make / call to action -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-cream border rounded-lg p-6">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-brown font-semibold">
      Cakes, Cookies, Donuts, Pies & More
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-dark-brown">
      Sweet Bakes Chicago makes treats for all occasions. Please take a look
      through our portfolio to see what we've done and what we can do, or let us
      design custom treats for you. The possibilities are endless!
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="/gallery"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-teal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-brand-grey-green">View Gallery</a>
      <a href="/contact"
        class="ml-3 inline-block border border-brand-teal text-brand-teal px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-brand-cream">Request
        a quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick links (flavors/pricing) -->
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <a href="/flavors"
      class="block p-4 border border-brand-teal rounded-lg bg-brand-cream hover:bg-brand-light-cream hover:shadow">
      <h4 class="font-heading text-brand-brown font-semibold">Flavors</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-brand-dark-brown">
        See our available signature flavors and seasonal options.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pricing"
      class="block p-4 border border-brand-teal rounded-lg bg-brand-cream hover:bg-brand-light-cream hover:shadow">
      <h4 class="font-heading text-brand-brown font-semibold">Pricing</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-brand-dark-brown">
        Layer cake and custom treat pricing and details.
      </p>
    </a>
  </section>
</main>
</Page>